\">Hardwood Fence</a> • <a href=\"/Iron_Fence\" title=\"Iron Fence\">Iron Fence</a> • <a href=\"/Stone_Fence\" title=\"Stone Fence\">Stone Fence</a> • <a href=\"/Wood_Fence\" title=\"Wood Fence\">Wood Fence</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Storage_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Storage</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Big_Chest\" title=\"Big Chest\">Big Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Big_Stone_Chest\" title=\"Big Stone Chest\">Big Stone Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Chest\" title=\"Chest\">Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Junimo_Chest\" title=\"Junimo Chest\">Junimo Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Fridge\" title=\"Mini-Fridge\">Mini-Fridge</a> • <a href=\"/Stone_Chest\" title=\"Stone Chest\">Stone Chest</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Signs\" title=\"Crafting\">Signs</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dark_Sign\" title=\"Dark Sign\">Dark Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Stone_Sign\" title=\"Stone Sign\">Stone Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Text_Sign\" title=\"Text Sign\">Text Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Wood_Sign\" title=\"Wood Sign\">Wood Sign</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Misc\" title=\"Crafting\">Misc</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Anvil\" title=\"Anvil\">Anvil</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee_Maker\" title=\"Coffee Maker\">Coffee Maker</a> • <a href=\"/Cookout_Kit\" title=\"Cookout Kit\">Cookout Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Deconstructor\" title=\"Deconstructor\">Deconstructor</a> • <a href=\"/Fairy_Dust\" title=\"Fairy Dust\">Fairy Dust</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Computer\" title=\"Farm Computer\">Farm Computer</a> • <a href=\"/Hopper\" title=\"Hopper\">Hopper</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Forge\" title=\"Mini-Forge\">Mini-Forge</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Jukebox\" title=\"Mini-Jukebox\">Mini-Jukebox</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Shipping_Bin\" title=\"Mini-Shipping Bin\">Mini-Shipping Bin</a> • <a href=\"/Sewing_Machine\" title=\"Sewing Machine\">Sewing Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Staircase\" title=\"Staircase\">Staircase</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_Blessings\" title=\"Statue Of Blessings\">Statue Of Blessings</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_The_Dwarf_King\" title=\"Statue Of The Dwarf King\">Statue Of The Dwarf King</a> •  <a href=\"/Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\">Telephone</a> • <a href=\"/Tent_Kit\" title=\"Tent Kit\">Tent Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">Tools</a> • <a href=\"/Workbench\" title=\"Workbench\">Workbench</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414074659\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.143 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.161 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 4598/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 15153/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3460/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 5507/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   89.815      1 -total\n 64.24%   57.694      1 Template:Infobox\n 30.41%   27.314      2 Template:Description\n 26.53%   23.827     12 Template:Name\n  4.99%    4.479      1 Template:Duration\n  4.47%    4.018      6 Template:History\n  4.45%    3.994      1 Template:Bundle\n  3.53%    3.169      5 Template:Season\n  3.43%    3.079      8 Template:Price\n  2.46%    2.205      6 Template:Version\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2087-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414074658 and revision id 191201\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Bee House\n|image2      = Bee House Full\n|image2spacing = true\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|season      = [[Spring]] • [[Summer]] • [[Fall]]\n|recipe      = {{Name|Farming Skill Icon|link=Farming|Level 3}}\n|ingredients = {{Name|Wood|40}}{{Name|Coal|8}}{{Name|Iron Bar|1}}{{Name|Maple Syrup|1}}\n|sellprice   = Cannot be sold\n}}\nThe '''Bee House''' is a type of [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]] used to make [[Honey]]. A Bee House is the reward for completing the {{Bundle|Fall Crops|18|y}}. Four Bee Houses can be obtained as the 19th prize from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|Prize Machine]] (50% chance).\n\nTo make honey, place a Bee House on the farm during any season but winter, and wait 4 nights. Bee houses can be placed indoors (''e.g.,'' in the [[Greenhouse]]) but will not produce honey there, regardless of any flowers within range. Bee houses placed outside the farm will produce wild honey every 4 days, but they will be destroyed if they are placed in a [[Crafting#Crafted goods outside the farm|villager's path]].\n\nA fully-grown and unharvested [[Flowers|flower]] within 5 tiles of a Bee House (including those grown in [[Garden Pot]]s) will cause it to produce flower honey, which always sells for more than flowerless Wild Honey. Flowers that are normally foraged (''i.e.,'' [[Crocus]] and [[Sweet Pea]]) do not affect the honey. Additionally, a [[Dandelion]] or [[Daffodil]] will not affect the honey as these items are classified as [[Foraging|forage]] rather than flowers.\n\nThe type of honey is established the moment it is harvested. If a Bee House has produced flower honey, but the flower is harvested before the honey, the honey will become wild honey. Similarly, if a Bee House has produced flowerless wild honey, but the honey is harvested after a flower bloomed in range, the harvested honey will be flower honey.\n\n==Products==\n<!--Note: This section is transcluded on the Artisan Goods page-->\n<section begin=\"beeproducts\" />\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Energy/Health\n!Processing Time<noinclude><ref name=\"processtime\"/></noinclude>\n!Availability\n!colspan=\"2\"|Base Sell Price\n|-\n|rowspan=\"8\"|[[File:Honey.png]]\n|rowspan=\"8\"|[[Honey]]\n|rowspan=\"8\"|{{Description|Honey}}\n|rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align: center;\"|''Inedible''\n|rowspan=\"8\"|{{Duration|4 Nights}}\n|class=\"no-wrap|All but [[Winter]]\n| Wild\n|{{Price|100}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{Season|Spring}}\n|{{Name|Tulip}}\n|{{Price|160}}\n|-\n|{{Name|Blue Jazz}}\n|{{Price|200}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|{{Season|Summer}}\n|{{Name|Sunflower}}\n|{{Price|260}}\n|-\n|{{Name|Summer Spangle}}\n|{{Price|280}}\n|-\n|{{Name|Poppy}}\n|{{Price|380}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{Season|Fall}}\n|{{Name|Sunflower}}\n|{{Price|260}}\n|-\n|{{Name|Fairy Rose}}\n|{{Price|680}}\n|}<section end=\"beeproducts\" />\n\n==Range==\n[[File:Bee House Range.png|200px|right|thumb|Flower zone indicator for modified [[Honey]].]]\nWith the exception of [[Crocus]] and [[Sweet Pea]], the Bee House can produce unique types of honey when it is within 5 tiles in any cardinal direction of a blooming flower (for a total area of 60, excluding the tile the Bee House is placed on). When there is more than one type of flower within range, the closest flower takes priority. At equal distances, the flower at the horizontal left takes priority, followed by the next clockwise flower.\n\n==Tips==\n* Planting flowers near Bee Houses on [[Ginger Island]] will produce flavored Honey year-round.\n* Garden Pots can be used in parts of the farm and Ginger Island farm where flowers can't be planted.\n* Filling all inventory slots but 1 will allow collecting honey without collecting any adjacent flowers.\n* Planting a [[Sunflower]] on Summer 20 will make sure flower honey can be harvested in early Fall\n\n==References==\n<references>\n  <ref name=\"processtime\">See <samp>Object::performDropDownAction</samp>, <samp>Object::DayUpdate</samp>, and <samp>Object::minutesElapsed</samp> in the game code. Bee House <samp>parentSheetIndex</samp> is <samp>10</samp>, as specified in <samp>Content\\Data\\BigCraftablesInformation.xnb</samp>.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Added honey from Sunflowers. Fixed lopsided flower range. Bee Houses can now be stacked in a player's [[inventory]] and in [[Chest|chests]].}}\n{{History|1.5|Fixed bug where processing time was affected by the time of day.}}\n{{History|1.5.2|Fixed bug where Honey could not be collected from Beehouses on Ginger Island farm in Winter.}}\n{{History|1.6|Removing a Bee House with honey ready for harvesting no longer drops the honey as \"Wild Honey\". Can now be obtained as a prize from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|Prize Machine]].}}\n{{History|1.6|Fixed bug where placing a Bee House on exactly Winter 28 will produce honey on Spring 4. A Bee house will now first produce honey on Spring 5}}\n{{History|1.6.6|Now produces flower honey with flowers in garden pots.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n[[Category:Bugs fixed in 1.5]]\n\n[[de:Bienenhaus]]\n[[es:Colmena]]\n[[fr:Ruche]]\n[[it:Arnia]]\n[[ja:ハチの巣箱]]\n[[ko:양봉장]]\n[[hu:Méhkaptár]]\n[[pt:Apiário]]\n[[ru:Улей]]\n[[tr:Arı Kovanı]]\n[[zh:蜂房]]"
    }
